Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.82,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0240,,{\fad(200,200)}Death PriPri Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得單調於是填充Pri的想法就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.84,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0049,,{\fad(200,200)}Death PriPri Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.68,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0226,,{\fad(200,200)}PriPriDeath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監獄和死神都跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.87,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,{\fad(0,200)}恰克desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death變成desu啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.56,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,{\fad(0,200)}飛鳥desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼好像在聽恰克與飛鳥的演唱會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.94,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,{\fad(0,200)}恰克&飛鳥desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別糾結恰克站哪裡行不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.19,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,{\fad(0,200)}飛鳥&恰克desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是恰克飛鳥漢堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.70,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,{\fad(0,200)}飛鳥&恰克&飛鳥desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.20,Banner,NTP,0300,0000,0130,,{\fad(0,200)}飛鳥&\N　　　恰克&\N　　　　　　飛鳥desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼DEATH又跑回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.33,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0180,,{\fad(0,200)}恰克是飛鳥DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後就決定這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.58,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0130,,恰克筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.01,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0130,,{\fad(0,200)}恰克筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰克筆記是啥  難道是那啥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字寫在上面就那啥的那啥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…  社團活動搞到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀短了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀短了什麼意思  我怎麼沒看到短
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格子都插爆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說監獄和死神都放棄了為什麼護肩還在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天月亮很詭異啊  這種夜晚肯定有事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個詭異的肩膀把月亮都擋住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你這麼愛畫肩膀格子還有個P用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狗大便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼無聊的場景要用大格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會畫橫長格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼恰克筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道是什麼就恰克筆記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.40,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飛鳥涼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  寫了飛鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰  恰克嗎  恰克寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鳥  稻葉  志村  阿格？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都是在組合裡比較搶眼一方的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:46.05,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3250-3000=250
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼寫人名字太恐怖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  不要讓別人誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了不該看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:56.92,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7*9=68 ……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你在計算些啥啊  為什麼要寫在分鏡裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘法表有這麼恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:17:01.10,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惡路木夢粹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠已經沒心情畫了啊  就別練習簽名了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人想要你們的簽名的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是死神琉子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波爐熱過再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的場面成了便簽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主滿臉都是炒飯啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你簽名終於完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡路木夢粹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死  死神？
